These are Puzzles for 3x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-1::.
There 2 different types of food: pumpkin, spinach
There are 2 different favourite colors: purple, brown
House: palace, cape-cod
1. the person who likes purple is on the right of the palace house##1
2. the person eating spinach is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2     |
| Food   | spinach    | pumpkin |
| Color         | brown | purple    |
| House     | palace     | cape-cod      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-2::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: dunhill, bluemaster
City: rome, nizza
The people have 2 different jobs:  chef, accountant
1. the accountant is on the left of the dunhill-smoker##1
2. the person traveling to rome is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |     2     |
| Cigar      | bluemaster  | dunhill   |
| City   | nizza | rome  |
| Job     | accountant   | chef |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-3::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  videographer, bartender
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, fanta
There are 2 different favourite colors: coral, turquise
1. the bartender is in an even position##4
2. the person drinking almond-milk is on the right of the person who likes coral##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |
| Job         | videographer   | bartender  |
| Beverage   | fanta | almond-milk  |
| Color         | coral   | turquise |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: zinnia, dahlia
2 different pets are kept: lizard, frog
There are 2 different nationalities: chinese, brazilian
1. the chinese is on the right of the owner of the frog##1
2. the person who growszinnia is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |
| Flower          | zinnia | dahlia |
| Pet   | frog   | lizard   |
| Nationality     | brazilian       | chinese      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-5::.
