.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-6::.
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: april, november
The people use 2 different means of transport: van, bike
There are 2 different favourite beverages: lemonade, fanta
1. the person driving the van is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the person drinking lemonade is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |
| Birthday         | april    | november    |
| Transport   | bike     | van      |
| Beverage         | lemonade | fanta |

