.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-7::.
2 different games are played: poker, go
House: tower, gothic-revival
There are 2 different favourite beverages: juice, water
1. the person drinking water is on the left of the tower house##1
2. the person drinking juice is on the left or right of the person drinking water##3
3. the person playing poker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |
| Game    | go | poker     |
| House     | gothic-revival | tower |
| Beverage   | water | juice    |

