.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-11::.
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: water-polo, weightlifting
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: november, june
There 2 different types of food: pomegranate, grapefruit
1. the person who's birthday is in june is on the left of the person eating pomegranate##1
2. the person who's birthday is in june is in an odd position##4
3. the person who's birthday is in november is on the right of the person who's sport is weightlifting##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |  2   |
| Sport           | weightlifting     | water-polo |
| Birthday   | june | november  |
| Food     | grapefruit      | pomegranate |

