.:: Puzzle 3x2-Level-4-15::.
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: havana, montecristo
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: marigold, azalea
There are 2 different favourite colors: mauve, chestnut
1. the person who likes chestnut is on the left of the person who likes mauve##1
2. the person who growsmarigold is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
3. the havana-smoker is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2      |
| Cigar         | montecristo | havana |
| Flower   | marigold     | azalea     |
| Color           | chestnut          | mauve     |

