There 2 different types of food: apricot, carrot
1. the person playing domino is in an odd position##4
2. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person eating carrot##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |    2    |
| Game   | domino | poker |
| Birthday   | march  | may  |
| Food     | carrot | apricot    |

 